trainers.name: Hiker Benny
trainers.dialogue: Are you heading to the mines?

trainers.name: Worker Joel
trainers.dialogue: The mine's abandoned, kid. Go home.

trainers.name: Guitarist Alex
trainers.dialogue: I'll roll over you with these tunes!

trainers.name: Gentleman Roderic
trainers.dialogue: You young ruffians have no respect.
